📌 Results
Performed comprehensive exploratory data analysis to understand Netflix user demographics and subscription behavior.
Visualized customer distributions across subscription plans, countries, devices, and gender.
Examined revenue patterns using descriptive statistics and comparative visualizations.
Applied statistical hypothesis testing, including Chi-Square, Shapiro-Wilk, and Levene's tests, to evaluate relationships between customer characteristics and monthly revenue.
Generated actionable insights into customer segmentation and revenue trends that can support data-driven business decisions.

📚 Future Improvements
Build predictive models to forecast customer churn or monthly revenue.
Apply clustering techniques for customer segmentation.
Develop interactive dashboards using Power BI or Tableau.
Perform time-series analysis if subscription history becomes available.
Incorporate additional customer engagement metrics such as watch time and viewing preferences.

